Marriot Vacations Worldwide Corporation (VAC) & Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide (HOT) Critical Contrast

					Posted by Tristan Rich on Jul 28th, 2017 // No Comments 




Marriot Vacations Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: VAC) and Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide (NYSE:HOT) are both consumer discretionary companies, but which is the better business? We will contrast the two businesses based on the strength of their risk, valuation, dividends, institutional ownership, analyst recommendations, earnings and profitabiliy. 
Analyst Recommendations


 Get Marriot Vacations Worldwide Corporation alerts:



