Marriot Vacations Worldwide Corporation has higher revenue and earnings than Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide. Marriot Vacations Worldwide Corporation is trading at a lower price-to-earnings ratio than Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide, indicating that it is currently the more affordable of the two stocks. 
